Package org.sbml.squeezer.sabiork.wizard.gui

The classes in this package are required for the graphical user interface of the SABIO-RK wizard.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    The abstract base class for all panels to be displayed in the SABIO-RK wizard.
    CardMatching
    A class that allows the manual matching of SBML components.
    CardMethod
    A class that allows to choose between the two different methods in the SABIO-RK wizard.
    CardReactionsA
    A class that allows the selection of reactions which are considered in the automatic search.
    CardReactionsM  
    CardSearchA
    A class that allows the automatic search in the SABIO-RK wizard.
    CardSearchM
    A class that allows the manual search in the SABIO-RK wizard.
    CardSearchResultsA  
    CardSearchResultsM  
    CardSummaryA
    A class that provides a short summary of the changes made by the SABIO-RK wizard.
    CardSummaryM
    A class that provides a short summary of the changes made by the SABIO-RK wizard.
    ComboBoxModelCaptions
    A class that allows to create a combo box with non-selectable captions.
    ComboBoxModelConstraints
    A class that provides the model of the combo box for selecting a constraint in the automatic search.
    ComboBoxModelReactionFilters
    A class that provides the model of the combo box for selecting a reaction filter.
    ComboBoxModelSearchItems
    A class that provides the model of the combo box for selecting a search item in the manual search.
    JComboBoxInterval
    A class that allows the creation of a combo box containing Double values from minimum to maximum (step size of 0.1).
    JComboBoxSearchField
    A class that provides a search field with suggestion support according to a given SABIO-RK query field.
    JComponentEtchedLine
    A class for drawing an etched horizontal line.
    JDialogWizard
    The GUI version of the SABIO-RK wizard.
    JPanelFilterOptions
    A class that provides the possibility to set the different filter options.
    TableCellRendererBooleans
    A class that renders Boolean values as disabled check boxes.
    TableCellRendererColorGradient
    A class that renders Double values as a color within a gradient.
    TableCellRendererpHValues
    A class that renders pH values as a color within a gradient.
    TableCellRendererReactions
    A class that renders a Reaction as a LaTeX formula.
    TableCellRendererSearchAResults
    A class that renders a complete TableModelSearchAResults according to the TableModelSearchAResults.SearchAResult within it.
    TableCellRendererTemperature
    A class that renders a temperature as a color within a gradient.
    TableModelReactions
    A class that allows the storage of Reaction.
    TableModelSearchAResults
    A class that allows the storage of TableModelSearchAResults.SearchAResult.
    TableModelSearchMResults
    A class that allows the storage of KineticLaw.
    TableModelSearchTerms
    A class that allows the storage of search terms.
